rows.label: campfev11_070_150_msg0001
rows.name: I can't wait to meet up with Kasumi.

rows.label: campfev11_070_150_msg0003
rows.name:
It's a straight shot from here,
so we shouldn't get lost.

rows.label: campfev11_070_150_msg0004
rows.name:
I wonder what Kasumi will think
when she meets Satahiko.

rows.label: campfev11_070_150_msg0007
rows.name:
Satahiko,
don't worry too much.
She's a very kind person.
